{"id":296397,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/06/维权网-安徽异议人士王翼翔因六四临近被限制人/","date":"2013-06-01T20:00:52Z","modified":"2013-06-01T20:00:52Z","title":"维权网 | 安徽异议人士王翼翔因六四临近被限制人身自由（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员方芳报道）因六四临近，安徽异议人士姑鹤（王翼翔）被严密监控，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>多位看守每天</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>班，每班</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3—4</span><span>人轮流在他家楼下，何时结束未知，外出时需坐看守人员的专车。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据了解，安徽马鞍山当涂县异议人士王翼翔（网名姑鹤），长期致力于宣传民主，被当地国保视为“危险分子”，常年被监控。每到敏感时期当地对他的监控都会升级。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">31</span><span>日</span><span>，由王翼翔原工作单位经贸公司和所居住的当涂县姑孰社区组成的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>多个人的监控小组，每天</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>班每班</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3-4</span><span>人，开始在王翼翔家楼下部署</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">24</span><span>小时对他的严密监控。当天上午，王翼翔要去菜市场买菜，刚到楼下就被守在楼道口的几名原单位同事和所在社区的工作人员拦住。王翼翔明白这是因为“六四”，他又被“上岗了”。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">     </span></div>\n<div><span>看守见王翼翔执意要外出，就打电话向上汇报。一辆标着司法的警车开来，开车的是县司法所所长。王翼翔无奈被迫坐着警车到附近的市场去买完菜又被送回家。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>图</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>、带王翼翔去买菜的警察</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>图</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>、驻守在王翼翔家楼下的看守</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-SS8bGHJvFFA/UaoVv8Ci5zI/AAAAAAAAiys/kEYXjpFTULc/s1600/1.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"232\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-SS8bGHJvFFA/UaoVv8Ci5zI/AAAAAAAAiys/kEYXjpFTULc/s1600/1.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-e-14Q0X3sSk/UaoVwYlXK3I/AAAAAAAAiy0/c946WZX2dFE/s1600/2.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-e-14Q0X3sSk/UaoVwYlXK3I/AAAAAAAAiy0/c946WZX2dFE/s320/2.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910,9282]}